    {{#> skincare-lifestyle
        title="Skincare is a lifestyle"
        text="Caring for your skin goes beyond the products you use. It’s about adopting habits that support your skin’s health every day. Our dermatologists recommend these expert tips to help you reach your skin goals even faster."
    }}
        <picture class="show">
            <img src="sections/isolated/skincare-lifestyle/images/sk_life_1.webp" alt="Protect your skin with SPF" />
        </picture>
        <picture>
            <img src="sections/isolated/skincare-lifestyle/images/sk_life_2.webp" alt="Reduce your sugar intake" />
        </picture>
        <picture>
            <img src="sections/isolated/skincare-lifestyle/images/good_fats.webp" alt="Nourish your skin with good fats" />
        </picture>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <button class="active" type="button">1</button>
                <h6>Protect your skin with SPF</h6>
                <p>Daily SPF is a must. It’s the easiest way to protect your skin from UV damage and prevent sun spots and dark spots from forming.</p>
                <img src="sections/isolated/skincare-lifestyle/images/sk_life_1.webp" alt="Protect your skin with SPF" />
            </li>
            <li>
                <button type="button">2</button>
                <h6>Reduce your sugar intake</h6>
                <p>Studies show that excess sugar and processed food can lead to increased inflammation which may worsen pigmentation.</p>
                <img src="sections/isolated/skincare-lifestyle/images/sk_life_2.webp" alt="Reduce your sugar intake" />
            </li>
            <li>
                <button type="button">3</button>
                <h6>Nourish your skin with good fats</h6>
                <p>Foods rich in omega-3s (like salmon and walnuts) support your skin’s elasticity and keep it looking firm and even.</p>
                <img src="sections/isolated/skincare-lifestyle/images/good_fats.webp" alt="Nourish your skin with good fats" />
            </li>
        </ul>
    {{/skincare-lifestyle }}

